{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tower of Madness blends tense exploration, gravity-defying environments, and chilling encounters to keep players on edge.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The average time to complete one play-through is 45 minutes.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177340/extras/FearfulAtmosphere.gif?t=1730591533\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Atmospheric Stylized Horror</strong>: Experience chilling environments filled with terrifying monsters, all brought to life through a unique and immersive art style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177340/extras/DefyGravity_eng.gif?t=1730591533\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gravity Manipulation</strong>: Use red magical glyphs to flip gravity and navigate between ceiling and floor. Progressing through mind-bending environments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by H.P. Lovecraft &amp; Stephen King's The Dark Tower series. An atmospheric, narrative-driven third-person horror game with a distinctive voice and unsettling twists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>More Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Player Choices Matter</strong>: Make choices in dialogue and Quick Time Events (QTEs) that determine the fate of John. Discover 1 of 3 different game endings based on your actions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Discover the past</strong>: Find 10 hidden notes to uncover the dark past of the tower. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collect &amp; Solve</strong>: Gather keys to unlock new areas and body parts to break through infinite looping hallways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Quick Time Events: </strong>QTE's keep you involved in the action and horror during cutscenes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Engaging Storyline</strong>: Follow John on his journey as he faces the darkest corners of his own mind. Fully voice-acted cutscenes add depth to this compelling narrative.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">John has lived all his life in a small, desert town. One fateful day, he starts hearing a sinister voice inside his head. This voice preempts a horrific event\u2014the murder of everyone John knows, right before his eyes. With nowhere else to turn, John is compelled to follow the voice, descending into a dry well that reveals a cavern containing an ominous, inverted floating tower. The voice tells John to follow his crows and ascend this mysterious structure. </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"You Found Wilhelm.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3177340/5f2264928289e68fcd69fe17e70f1ce477277b3a.jpg"},{"name":"This is not a platformer.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3177340/1af242c96968cae01226e5ff9477c881ebdbf961.jpg"},{"name":"Turn your world upside down.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3177340/ffe2c15ed7a1473cce6619d54ac928dae62c35d5.jpg"},{"name":"Find a key item.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3177340/ca6f43acbacf49307e12e5b7ba938a8aeb054fe6.jpg"},{"name":"Break the loop.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3177340/720884dd32068947f0fe5968f288175731a9700e.jpg"},{"name":"One note.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3177340/56fb7c2b06b158ef7c7458d64a4674cbc83ace90.jpg"},{"name":"Hints of the past.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3177340/39da34cce12b2b32e4d178a0f6f6e38efca776dd.jpg"},{"name":"The past revealed.","path":"htt